  description="Browse high-level IELTS & CELPIP lessons: grammar, vocabulary, writing, and speaking. Clear explanations plus practice tasks."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="stack">
      <span class="pill">üìö Lessons ‚Ä¢ Band 7+ Focus</span>
      <h1>Lessons</h1>
      <p class="muted" style="max-width: 70ch;">
        Choose a category to explore high-level lessons for IELTS &amp; CELPIP. Each lesson includes clear explanations and
        practice tasks.
      </p>

